</blockquote>

<p>Are you sure about that? Your emotions don't ask you for permission before they make associations.</p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_28jk"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_28jk" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_28jk')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_28jk" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_28jk')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_28jk" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/2ev/rationality_quotes_july_2010/28jk?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="parent_t1_28jk" href="#28j9" class="bylink">Parent</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_28jk" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_28jk')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_28jk class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_28jk" class="child" ><div id="siteTable_t1_28jk" class="sitetable"><div id="ajaxHook_t1_28jk" class="ajaxhook"></div><div id="thingrow_t1_28k3" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_28k3" class="parent"><a name="28k3" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_28k3" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_28k3" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_28k3" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/Blueberry/">Blueberry</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">04 July 2010 04:53:19AM</span><span class="votes " >0 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_28k3'] = ['-1 points', '0 points', '1 point' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_28k3')">[+] (6 children)</a></div><div id="display_t1_28k3" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_28k3" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/Blueberry/">Blueberry</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">04 July 2010 04:53:19AM</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_28k3'>0 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_28k3'] = ['-1 points', '0 points', '1 point' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_28k3')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_28k3" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><p>I can't tell if this is wordplay based on the ambiguity in the quoted sentence (in which case, I like the joke :) ) or if you're serious. If you're serious, then yes, I'm sure: while emotions may not ask me for permission, I'm aware of what they're associated with.</p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_28k3"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_28k3" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_28k3')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_28k3" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_28k3')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_28k3" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/2ev/rationality_quotes_july_2010/28k3?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="parent_t1_28k3" href="#28jk" class="bylink">Parent</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_28k3" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_28k3')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_28k3 class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_28k3" class="child" ><div id="siteTable_t1_28k3" class="sitetable"><div id="ajaxHook_t1_28k3" class="ajaxhook"></div><div id="thingrow_t1_28kw" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_28kw" class="parent"><a name="28kw" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_28kw" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_28kw" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_28kw" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/red75/">red75</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">04 July 2010 08:09:27AM</span><span class="votes " >0 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_28kw'] = ['-1 points', '0 points', '1 point' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_28kw')">[+] (0 children)</a></div><div id="display_t1_28kw" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_28kw" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/red75/">red75</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">04 July 2010 08:09:27AM</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_28kw'>0 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_28kw'] = ['-1 points', '0 points', '1 point' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_28kw')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_28kw" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><p>Strange. I have associations for green (foliage, leafs), yellow (sun), blue(water). Red requires conscious effort to select domain for association to pop up.</p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_28kw"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_28kw" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_28kw')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_28kw" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_28kw')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_28kw" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/2ev/rationality_quotes_july_2010/28kw?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="parent_t1_28kw" href="#28k3" class="bylink">Parent</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_28kw" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_28kw')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_28kw class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_28kw" class="child" ></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div><div id="thingrow_t1_28kt" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_28kt" class="parent"><a name="28kt" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_28kt" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_28kt" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><em>Comment deleted</em>&#32;<span class="comment-date">04 July 2010 07:49:41AM</span><a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_28kt')">[+]