mment-content"><div class="md"><p>Well, it would have to be a popup box that interrupts whatever you're currently thinking about. It grabs focus, to continue the analogy.</p>

<p>Does pain produce muscle memory? I haven't heard that before.</p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_28d4"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_28d4" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_28d4')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_28d4" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_28d4')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_28d4" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/2ev/rationality_quotes_july_2010/28d4?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="parent_t1_28d4" href="#28d3" class="bylink">Parent</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_28d4" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_28d4')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_28d4 class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_28d4" class="child" ><div id="siteTable_t1_28d4" class="sitetable"><div id="ajaxHook_t1_28d4" class="ajaxhook"></div><div id="thingrow_t1_28lo" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_28lo" class="parent"><a name="28lo" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_28lo" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_28lo" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_28lo" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/xamdam/">xamdam</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">04 July 2010 01:04:28PM</span><span class="votes " >1 point</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_28lo'] = ['0 points', '1 point', '2 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_28lo')">[+] (0 children)</a></div><div id="display_t1_28lo" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_28lo" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/xamdam/">xamdam</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">04 July 2010 01:04:28PM</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_28lo'>1 point</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_28lo'] = ['0 points', '1 point', '2 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_28lo')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_28lo" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><p>Maybe a popup would be better, but until we can hack our brains the question remains whether you're better off with shame as a learning mechanism.</p>

<p>Does pain produce learning? Probably yes.</p>

<p><a href="http://www.nytimes.com/1991/08/27/news/pain-and-learning-may-be-close-cousins-in-chain-of-evolution.html?pagewanted=all" rel="nofollow">http://www.nytimes.com/1991/08/27/news/pain-and-learning-may-be-close-cousins-in-chain-of-evolution.html?pagewanted=all</a></p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_28lo"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_28lo" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_28lo')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_28lo" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_28lo')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_28lo" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/2ev/rationality_quotes_july_2010/28lo?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="parent_t1_28lo" href="#28d4" class="bylink">Parent</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_28lo" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_28lo')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_28lo class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_28lo" class="child" ></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div><div id="thingrow_t1_28bj" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_28bj" class="parent"><a name="28bj" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_28bj" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_28bj" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_28bj" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/NancyLebovitz/">NancyLebovitz</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">02 July 2010 05:16:48PM</span><span class="votes " >11 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_28bj'] = ['10 points', '11 po